<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَنّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنْ كَانَ فِي شَيْءٍ فَفِي الْفَرَسِ وَالْمَرْأَةِ وَالْمَسْكَنِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
